Package org.apache.taverna.server.usagerecord.xml.urf2 Description

Open Grid Forum GFD.204 Usage Record Format JAXB elements.

JAXB beans for the Usage Record Format 2.0 as described by https://www.ogf.org/ (OGF) specification GFD.204 serialized in the namespace http://schema.ogf.org/urf/2013/04/urf

This package provides the underlying JAXB elements and types for marshalling and unmarshalling XML according to the Usage Record Format.

The classes in this package are derived from the XML schema in GDF.204 section 14
